    "The findings align with this goal and provide important insights into how the IAEA regulatory framework can accommodate the rapid advancement and integration of AI technology.",
    "These discoveries not only fulfill the paper's purpose but also make significant contributions to international discussions on AI regulation.",
    "The analysis offers important perspectives into how AI could be integrated within the IAEA's existing regulatory framework.",
    "The study explored concrete cases of how AI technology could be applied to the IAEA's nuclear safety and security regulation.",
    "Specifically, it analyzed how interactions could occur in areas like AI systems' risk assessment capabilities, accident prevention, and operational efficiency improvements."
